  <chapter id="anjuta-architecture">
  	<title>Anjuta Architecture</title>
	<para>
		libanjuta defines a component-based plugin framework for Anjuta. In
		its core is the shell (#AnjutaShell) in which all plugins are loaded.
		Plugins can also merge thier UI and preferences in #AnjutaUI and
		#AnjutaPreferences, respectively.
	</para>
	<para>
		Plugins subclass #AnjutaPlugin abstract class and interact with
		each other using interfaces. They can also export objects with
		<emphasis>Values Sytem</emphasis> in #AnjutaShell.
	</para>
